 \dfrac{10a+b}{9} = (a+j).kkk... 
(j,k)= \begin{cases} (0,a+b) & \text{if }a+b \in \{0,1,2,...,8\} \\ (1,a+b-9) & \text{if }a+b \in \{9,10,11,...,17\} \\ (2,a+b-18) & \text{if }a+b =18 \\ \end{cases}
